This app is a self-contained GitOps reconciler that materializes authoritative
IdP-group membership into managed Matrix room membership through a narrowly scoped
access-manager Matrix client identity (docs/adr/0009-agent-authorization-model.md).
It is deliberately NOT bundled into apps/matrix-a2a-bridge.

It embeds the following third-party components, all under permissive licenses:

  - maunium.net/go/mautrix              MPL-2.0
  - github.com/caarlos0/env             MIT
  - github.com/prometheus/client_golang Apache-2.0
  - gopkg.in/yaml.v3                    MIT / Apache-2.0

No AGPL dependency is present. Never add one. The Matrix client uses only normal
Client-Server API endpoints (resolve alias, room state, profile lookup, invite,
kick, ban); it holds no Synapse-admin or MAS admin credential.
